= ModelTesting

Scripts for testing aspects of the LSDMixingModel.

These include

. Some scripts testing the LSDMixingModel cosmo code against analytical soultion from existing papers.
.. 'CRN_production_w_depth.py`: Calculates cosmogenic production with depth using equation 20 from  https://pubs.geoscienceworld.org/msa/rimg/article/47/1/731/235418/cosmic-ray-produced-noble-gases-in-terrestrial[Niedermann, 2002].
.. 'CRN_production_w_depth_erosion_lal.py`: Calculates cosmogenic production with depth incorporating erosion using equation 11 from  https://www-sciencedirect-com.ezproxy.is.ed.ac.uk/science/article/pii/S0012821X05003419[Lal and Chen, 2005].
..'CRN_production_w_depth_mixing_depth_brown.py`: Calculates cosmogenic production with depth incorporating mixing using equation 5 from  https://www-sciencedirect-com.ezproxy.is.ed.ac.uk/science/article/pii/0012821X9400249X[Brown et al, 1995].
.. 'CRN_production_w_depth_mixing_no_erosion_lal.py`: Calculates cosmogenic production with depth incorporating mixing using equation 13 from  https://www-sciencedirect-com.ezproxy.is.ed.ac.uk/science/article/pii/S0012821X05003419[Lal and Chen, 2005]. note the erratum equation is used instead of the incorrect one within the paper.

